pma:database.name: adminpanel
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `register` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `username` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `password` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `usertype` varchar(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=31 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `student` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `fname` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `occupation` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `duration` varchar(50) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
